---
title: "US47 — Create / manage service listings"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ServicesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>PublishService
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertService
  A->>B: enter title, PricingModel, PriceCents, tap PUBLISH
  alt new listing
    B->>C: publish(listing)
    C->>E: insertExpertService(listing)
    E-->>C: ExpertService (status = live)
    B-->>A: visible in marketplace
  else edit / archive
    B->>C: update(listing)
    C->>E: updateExpertService(serviceId, changes)
    E-->>C: ExpertService (status = archived)
    B-->>A: hidden from marketplace
  end
  note over E: insertExpertService / updateExpertService via SupabaseGateway → expert_services (RLS).<br/>PriceCents stored only — payment simulated
